videos.description: Alex Robinson finds a cutting to Vladimir Brodziansky who jams it home for TCU.
videos.headline: Robinson's nice pass leads to Brodziansky dunk

videos.description: Kenrich Williams show off his athleticism as he puts in the missed shot for TCU.
videos.headline: Williams flies in  for putback plus a foul

videos.description: Alex Robinson's nice pass to Vladimir Brodziansky leads to an easy dunk for TCU.
videos.headline: Robinson finds Brodziansky for a dunk

videos.description: Alex Robinson's 17 assists leads TCU to a win over Iowa State.
videos.headline: Robinson credits teammates for big game
